# IMP-0700

# Hypervisor Public API

Status: Draft

Version: 0.1

Depends on:

All previous IMP documents.

---

# 1. Purpose

This document defines the public API exposed by the AiDN Hypervisor.

The API provides external control of the Hypervisor.

Internal services SHALL NOT communicate through this API.

The API exists exclusively for external clients.

---

# 2. Design Principles

### API-1

The API SHALL be stateless.

---

### API-2

Every operation SHALL map to exactly one Command.

---

### API-3

The API SHALL NOT expose implementation details.

---

### API-4

Every response SHALL be deterministic.

---

